title: No version found for model in path
body:
I started with Python version of ovms, but I couldn't deploy it in recent tests.
I executed the following command according to the document, but always no version found for model in path
Is there a problem with my directory location?


link is https://github.com/openvinotoolkit/model_server/blob/main/docs/ovms_quickstart.md
`
docker pull openvino/model_server:2021.3

curl --create-dirs https://download.01.org/opencv/2021/openvinotoolkit/2021.1/open_model_zoo/models_bin/1/face-detection-retail-0004/FP32/face-detection-retail-0004.xml https://download.01.org/opencv/2021/openvinotoolkit/2021.1/open_model_zoo/models_bin/1/face-detection-retail-0004/FP32/face-detection-retail-0004.bin -o model/1/face-detection-retail-0004.xml -o model/1/face-detection-retail-0004.bin

docker run -d -u $(id -u):$(id -g) -v $(pwd)/model:/models/face-detection -p 9007:9007 openvino/model_server:latest \
--model_path /models/face-detection --model_name face-detection --port 9007 --log_level DEBUG --shape auto

docker logs -f containerid
`
